{
  "texts": [
    "Taking the latent variables as input, the decoder can generate new samples.",
    "Different from the GANs that employ the generator network to fit the distribution of training samples, VAEs generate new samples via sampling from the learned distribution of training samples.• Diffusion models (DFMs).",
    "DFMs are made up of diffusion and denoising [213].",
    "Diffusion is a Markov chain and the random noise is added to the training samples in each time step.",
    "The purpose of denoising is to recover the training samples polluted by the random noise via adjusting the hyperparameters."
  ]
}